text: "Island Girl" is a 1975 song by Elton John and is the leading single from his 10th studio album Rock of the Westies. It went to number 1 in the United States, number 14 in the United Kingdom, number 12 in Australia and number 4 in New Zealand and Canada. ==References== Category:1975 songs Category:Elton John songs Category:Disco songs
title: Island Girl
